Package common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICommand
    Interface for communications from GUI to Logic, and from GUI to Client.
    IGameState
    Interface for communications from Logic to GUI, and from Logic to Server.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    This class is used for notifying the game logic about events happened on the GUI.
    Coordinate
    Class to store 2 dimensional coordinates.
    DynamicField
    This class stores the actual coordinates, and the necessary movement delta coordinates of a dynamic field.
    GameState
    This class is used for notifying the GUI about changes in the map, player positions, game phase, etc.
